EN: Declaring an isolationist policy could lead to tense international relations.

ZH: 过去的王朝曾多次实行闭关锁国政策。
EN: Past dynasties have often practiced isolationism.

ZH: 他们的闭关锁国政策导致了经济的停滞。
EN: Their isolationist policy led to economic stagnation.

ZH: 闭关锁国的结果可能会带来贫穷和不稳定。
EN: The consequence of isolationism could bring poverty and instability.

ZH: 古代中国多次因为闭关锁国而错过了机遇。
EN: Ancient China missed opportunities many times due to isolationism.

ZH: 闭关锁国往往会导致国际社会的孤立。
EN: Isolationism often leads to the isolation of the international community.

